{"id":"compose-seed-inventory","domain":"tools","difficulty":"medium","pass":true,"score":1,"reasoning":"All 5 MSS fields match exactly","expected":{"contentType":"tools","structure":"list","mechanics":["sort","filter"],"boundary":"none","scale":2},"actual":"```json\n{\"contentType\":\"tools\",\"structure\":\"list\",\"mechanics\":[\"sort\",\"filter\"],\"boundary\":\"none\",\"scale\":2}\n```\n\n**Reasoning:**\n- **contentType: `tools`** — Matches your existing garden planner. Both are utility modules for gardening management and will auto-group in your garden workspace.\n- **structure: `list`** — Seeds organized in a defined sequence (by planting season), which is a list pattern.\n- **mechanics: `[\"sort\",\"filter\"]`** — You explicitly want sorting by season and filtering by crop type.\n- **boundary: `none`** — Personal inventory data, same privacy model as your planner.\n- **scale: 2** — Object Group containing multiple seed entries (S1 objects), same level as your planner. Two S2 modules will compose into an S3 block (your garden workspace) when connected.","durationMs":4288}
